"title": "3203: Holy Spirit, and assurance",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3203: holy spirit, and assurance",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit assures believers of their standing in Christ and their eternal salvation.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit makes an individual a member of Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9\">ROM 8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:12\">1CO 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:17\">1CO 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:8\">1TH 4:8</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit assures believers that they have been born anew</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:29\">ROM 2:29</a></strong> <em>The true sign of belonging to God is not any outward mark on the body, but the regenerating power of the Spirit within.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:5-John3:6\">JHN 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:6\">ROM 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:6\">2CO 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:29\">GAL 4:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:5–3:7</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit assures believers that they are God's children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14-Rom8:16\">ROM 8:14–8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit assures believers that God loves them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit assures believers that Jesus Christ lives in them and they in him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:13\">1JN 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:24\">1JN 3:24</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit assures believers that God's power is within them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:5\">GAL 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>The fruit of the Spirit is evidence of the believer's standing in Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15-Matt7:20\">MAT 7:15–7:20</a></strong> <em>Spiritual gifts alone are not a sufficient basis for assurance.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:52\">ACT 13:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6\">ROM 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:6\">2CO 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal5:25\">GAL 5:16–5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit assures believers of the significance of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:10-1Cor2:12\">1CO 2:10–2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:14-2Cor3:17\">2CO 3:14–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:5\">EPH 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit is the first instalment of the believer's inheritance in the kingdom of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:21–1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit assures believers of their final victory in Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:5\">2CO 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15-Rom8:17\">ROM 8:15–8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:23\">ROM 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:14\">EPH 1:14</a></p>",
